---
title: Hearty Mushroom & Leek Lasagne with Parmesan White Sauce
description: Lasagnes are a much-loved dinner time staple and with a stack of shrooms’, veggies and a delightfully creamy sauce it will
become unbeatable. The sharp Parmesan stirred through the sauce brings an extra zap of flavour that you’ll adore.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
